{1\over AB}+{PB\over AB\cdot PC}={BC\over AB}\cdot{1\over PC}
\frac{PB}{PC}=\frac{AB}{AC},
\frac{1}{AB}+\frac{1}{AC}=\frac{1}{AB}+\frac{PB}{AB\cdot PC}=\frac{1}{AB}\left(1+\frac{PB}{PC}\right)=\frac{1}{AB}\cdot\frac{BC}{PC}.
