\frac{1}{2}PB\sin(θ)+\frac{1}{2}PC\sin(θ) = \frac{1}{2}BC\sin(2θ)
\sin(2θ)= 2\sin(θ)cos(θ) \\ \Rightarrow PB+PC= 2BC\cos(θ)
\Rightarrow \frac{1}{C}+\frac{1}{B} =2\frac{\cos(θ)}{P}
